OL,5, The first minister has revealed that he
OL,6, has received threats to his physical   
OL,7, safety over Wales' new 20mph law.      
OL,9,FMark Drakeford told the Senedd that he 
OL,10,Fhad been sent "vile" messages and      
OL,11,Fsupporters of the lower speed limit    
OL,12,Fdeserved to be treated with respect.   
OL,14,FPolice said they were investigating    
OL,15,F"reports of malicious communications"  
OL,16,Fsent to the first minister.            
OL,18,FWales was the first UK country to cut  
OL,19,Fthe default speed in built-up areas    
OL,20,Ffrom 30mph to 20mph earlier this month.
